crontab makes it possible to run the program at a set time everyday (12.00 in this example).
Steps:
1. Turn Data-mining-Property.py into Data-mining-Property.command
2. Open Terminal and type chmod 777 /path/Data-mining-Property.py
3. Still in terminal write crontab -e
4. Paste: 12 00 * * * /path/Data-mining-Property.command
5. press ":" then write "wq"
Done.
